cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with 3D reconstruction from stereo event-camera data. It could also belong to Robotics (cs.RO) as the method is designed for use in Simultaneous Localization and Mapping (SLAM) applications. Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) are also possible categories as the paper proposes an energy function optimization and a probabilistic depth-fusion strategy, which are common techniques in these fields.
